00:35.522 --> 00:53.780
We're in you shall greatly rejoice, if now you must be for a little time made sorrowful in diverse temptations, that the trial of your faith much more precious than gold, which is tried by the fire, may be found unto praise and glory and honor.

00:53.820 --> 01:04.530
At the appearance of Jesus Christ our Lord, words from today's epistle from St. Peter's letter, in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Ghost, amen.

01:05.634 --> 01:29.384
On this feast day of the chair of St. Peter, let's consider a few things about Lourdes, France, and the apparitions that took place there in 1858, as well as its connection to the papacy, and finally a few notes about the papacy itself, given that we have a conclave coming up upon us.

01:31.367 --> 01:34.130
Okay, first, five days ago,

01:34.402 --> 01:43.555
Our lady came to St. Bernadette for the third time and asked the little saint if she would come to the grotto for fifteen days in a row.

