Because she was to be given the divine privilege of motherhood of Christ.

28:22.915 --> 28:24.978
Now, likened to the Annunciation,

28:27.490 --> 28:41.289
Our blessed Lord says to Simon Peter, blessed Artha, as Mary was blessed because she was to be the mother of Christ, the head of the mystical body.

